---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Full Service Automation — Formic"
  description="Full Service Automation is Formic's Robots-as-a-Service model — equipment, software, parts, service, and 24/7 support under one fixed monthly fee. No CapEx, contracted performance, weeks to deploy."
  ogTitle="Full Service Automation — Formic"
  ogDescription="Robots-as-a-Service from Formic. Equipment, software, service, and support under one fixed monthly fee. No CapEx, contracted performance, weeks to deploy."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/full-service" slot="head" />
  <style is:global slot="head">
    .fs-bgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px}
    .fs-bcell{background:var(--white);padding:32px 28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
    .fs-bcell .fs-ptag{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--orange);text-transform:uppercase;margin:0}
    .fs-bcell h3{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:20px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black);margin:0}
    .fs-bcell p{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.6;color:var(--mgrey);margin:0}
    .fs-bcell .fs-plink{margin-top:auto;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);text-decoration:none;padding-top:10px}
    .fs-yt-wrap{position:relative;width:100%;max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;aspect-ratio:16/9;background:#000;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
    .fs-yt-wrap iframe{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;border:0}
    .fs-qgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey)}
    .fs-qcard{background:var(--white);padding:36px 34px;text-decoration:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;color:inherit}
    .fs-qcard blockquote{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:18px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.5;color:var(--black);margin:0;letter-spacing:-.005em}
    .fs-qcard .fs-qattr{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey)}
    .fs-qcard .fs-qlink{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);margin-top:auto}
  </style>

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span>Full Service Automation
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Full Service Automation</div>
    <h1>Everything.<br><em>Included.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">Full Service Automation is Formic's Robots-as-a-Service model — equipment, programming, deployment, 24/7 support, and production data, all under one fixed monthly fee. No CapEx, no integrators to coordinate, no surprise costs. We scope your line, build the system, install it, and stay on it for life.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/Focus-7603.jpg">
        <source src="/Formic-Header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-cap">Full Service Automation · what's included</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — What is Full Service Automation?</div>
      <h2>Robots-as-a-Service, <em>turnkey from day one</em>.</h2>
      <p>Full Service Automation is the complete solution for manufacturers who want robotics without becoming a robotics shop. Formic scopes your line, builds the system, ships and installs it, and stays on the line for life — every piece of it covered by one fixed monthly fee.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>No CapEx — operational expense, not a capital project</li>
        <li>Weeks to deploy, not the 12–18 months a traditional integration takes</li>
        <li>Equipment, software, parts, and service — all under one agreement</li>
        <li>Performance and uptime SLAs written into every contract</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Get a quote →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Focus-7603.jpg" alt="Formic team scoping a customer line for Full Service Automation" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Scope · Build · Run</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px">
    <div class="db-tag">02 — The Three Pillars</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,56px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05;color:var(--black);margin:8px 0 6px">Three pillars, <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">one agreement</em>.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:16px;font-weight:300;color:var(--dgrey);max-width:720px;margin:8px 0 0">Equipment, parts and service, and the technology that ties them together — covered under one Full Service agreement.</p>
    <div class="fs-bgrid">
      <div class="fs-bcell">
        <div class="fs-ptag">01 · Equipment &amp; Systems</div>
        <h3>The hardware on your floor</h3>
        <p>Case packers, palletizers, machine-tending cells, wrappers, and AMRs — designed, built, and shipped by Formic. Standardized, modular, and swappable as your line evolves.</p>
        <a class="fs-plink" href="/solutions">See solutions →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="fs-bcell">
        <div class="fs-ptag">02 · Parts &amp; Service</div>
        <h3>24/7 support, every shift</h3>
        <p>Bilingual 24/7 tech support, a regional Field Service Engineer network, contracted SLAs, and 100%-included corrective and preventive maintenance — parts and labor.</p>
        <a class="fs-plink" href="/#cta">Talk to engineering →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="fs-bcell">
        <div class="fs-ptag">03 · Technology &amp; Software</div>
        <h3>Formic Production Intelligence</h3>
        <p>Real-time OEE, throughput, and cycle-time data through FPI; remote diagnostics and OTA upgrades through Formic Cortex and Core — every customer benefits from every deployment.</p>
        <a class="fs-plink" href="/magic">Inside the platform →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">Get started, the easy way</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,56px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05;color:var(--white);margin:8px 0 28px">Success <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">from day one</em>.</h2>
    <div class="fs-yt-wrap">
      <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SD0UMnNYR1E" title="Formic Full Service Automation" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dgrey">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">Why choose Full Service Automation</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,68px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 12px">$0 CapEx. Flexible kit. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">Contracted performance.</em></h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:16px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(240,245,241,.6);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto 52px">Three reasons manufacturers pick Formic over a traditional CapEx purchase, a lease, or a third-party integrator.</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);text-align:left">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:34px 28px">
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:rgba(255,145,0,.6);margin-bottom:14px">01</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:24px;font-weight:600;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:4px">$0 CapEx</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);margin-bottom:18px">Monthly payment</div>
        <ul class="feats" style="margin:0"><li>No upfront investment — operational expense, not a capital project</li><li>Accessible to every manufacturer, no engineering team required</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:34px 28px">
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:rgba(255,145,0,.6);margin-bottom:14px">02</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:24px;font-weight:600;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:4px">Equipment Swapping</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);margin-bottom:18px">Same agreement</div>
        <ul class="feats" style="margin:0"><li>Swap or upgrade equipment as your production needs change</li><li>Scale up or down without re-negotiating your contract</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:34px 28px">
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:rgba(255,145,0,.6);margin-bottom:14px">03</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:24px;font-weight:600;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:4px">Contracted Performance</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);margin-bottom:18px">Credits if missed</div>
        <ul class="feats" style="margin:0"><li>Uptime and performance SLAs written into every contract</li><li>Performance credits if SLA metrics are missed — we're invested in your success</li></ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:96px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="db-tag">Take the complexity out of automation</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,56px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05;color:var(--black);margin:8px 0 32px">In their <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">own words</em>.</h2>
    <div class="fs-qgrid">
      <a class="fs-qcard" href="/stories/camerons-coffee">
        <blockquote>"Formic removes all the anxiety of a traditional equipment purchase. We like that they provide the entire solution, including committed uptime and service."</blockquote>
        <div class="fs-qattr">Cameron's Coffee</div>
        <span class="fs-qlink">Read the story →</span>
      </a>
      <a class="fs-qcard" href="/stories/uncle-crumbles">
        <blockquote>"With Formic, we were able to say 'Let's get it in here now' and start our automation plan quickly. If our customers want something different, we have the option to change and shift quickly."</blockquote>
        <div class="fs-qattr">Uncle Crumbles</div>
        <span class="fs-qlink">Read the story →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>No CapEx. No Risk.<br><em>No Problems.</em></h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get a Quote</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
